        <mxCell id="8GndnygLBg9SclneiAOy-4" parent="1" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;🔢 Django sends the question to &lt;strong&gt;Titan&lt;/strong&gt; (in Bedrock) → gets the query embedding.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;🔍 Django searches &lt;strong&gt;pgvector&lt;/strong&gt; with that embedding.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;📤 pgvector &lt;strong&gt;returns the matching chunks&lt;/strong&gt; to Django.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;📝 Django sends &lt;strong&gt;prompt + chunks&lt;/strong&gt; to &lt;strong&gt;Claude&lt;/strong&gt; (in Bedrock, via Guardrails).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;✅ Claude returns the &lt;strong&gt;grounded answer + citation&lt;/strong&gt; (post-Guardrails) → back to the user.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;IGW + ALB/WAF in a public subnet, Django + Postgres + (Bedrock via VPC endpoint) in a private subnet = a textbook secure VPC.&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="220" width="490" x="300" y="900" as="geometry" />
